creator: Bushel
descriptionHtml:
Growers with Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator can access their account information any time of the day, from anywhere.

Scale Tickets | Contracts | Commodity Balances | Prepaids | Cash Bids & Market Information

See your scale tickets as they roll in, no more compiling at the end of long days. Filter your tickets and export for easy and accurate reporting.

Check contract status or sign immediately to lock in the best grain prices, and check the percentage fulfilled towards those contracts. Review your open and closed contracts at any time.

See account information on all of your accounts with us, and give and remove access securely.

And, the Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator app is free to use, forever.

title: Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator

creator: Bushel
descriptionHtml:
The Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator app is an essential mobile solution that connects your operation to your grain facility, providing real-time, actionable information to help you manage and grow your business.

With a robust toolset that's constantly evolving to meet the demands of the modern grower, your Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator app is built with powerful features to help you save time and maximize profits, including:

Cash Bids: View location's cash bids in real-time
Futures: See Grains, Feed, Livestock and Ethanol futures listed in order of your preference
Scale Tickets: Easily access and filter scale tickets
Contracts: See contract balances, including locked-in basis/futures prices
Commodity Balances: View your commodity inventories
Settlements: See information on your payments, when and where you need it

The Wheaton Dumont Coop Elevator app is free, secure, and backed by the industry-leading Bushel platform.
